# Automated Warehouse System

## AGV Navigation Failure

Incident ID:
AGV-NAV-014

Symptoms

- Vehicle stops unexpectedly
- Navigation map mismatch
- Laser scanner warnings

Recovery Procedure

1. Restart localization service.
2. Verify LiDAR calibration.
3. Load latest warehouse map.
4. Reset navigation controller.
5. Perform autonomous test route.

Required Tools

- Diagnostic Tablet
- Ethernet Cable
- Laser Alignment Kit
